orever","pricingPage.upToXSeats":"Up to %param1% seats","pricingPage.pickYourPlan":"Pick your plan","pricingPage.completeFeaturesList":"Complete features list","pricingPage.seeCompleteFeaturesList":"See complete features list","pricingPage.hideCompleteFeaturesList":"Hide complete features list","pricingPage.month":"month","pricingPage.year":"year","pricingPage.mostPopular":"Most Popular","pricingPage.comingSoon":"Coming Soon","pricingPage.monthAndSeatIndication":"Per seat, per month","pricingPage.seatPeriod":"Per seat / month","pricingPage.perSeat":"Per seat","pricingPage.perMonth":"Per month","pricingPage.perMonthSlash":"/ month","pricingPage.seatOver":"seat /","pricingPage.free":"free","pricingPage.forever":"forever","pricingPage.total":"Total","pricingPage.total.withNumber":"Total %param1% / month","pricingPage.total.withNumber.yearly":"Total %param1% / year","pricingPage.round_note":"The actual price per seat is %param1%, listed price is rounded up to the nearest whole number","pricingPage.faq.questions":"Questions?","pricingPage.faq.new.freeVersion.question":"Is there a free version of monday.com?","pricingPage.faq.new.freeVersion.answer":"If you would like to access monday.com beyond the 14-day trial, you can do so through purchasing a plan. If you are a \u003ca href='https://forms.monday.com/forms/9f862eef0081db8c8b6e1f9f574bdabf' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003enonprofit\u003c/a\u003e, you may be qualified to access monday.com for free or at a discount by filling out the designated forms.","pricingPage.faq.new.freeVersion.answer.for_free_tier":"Yes! Our Individual Plan is for independent professionals looking to keep track of their tasks and work. If you are interested in using only the most essential features of monday.com, this is the plan for you!","pricingPage.faq.new.cost.question":"How much does monday.com cost?","pricingPage.faq.new.cost.answer":"monday.com starts from $24 per month for 3 users and goes up from there based on your chosen plan and team size. If you are over 40 users, you can \u003ca href='https://monday.com/sales/contact-us?from=pricing\u0026source=Website%20-%20Contact%20Sales' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003erequest a quote\u003c/a\u003e to get an exact price.","pricingPage.faq.new.monthly.question":"Can you pay for monday.com monthly?","pricingPage.faq.new.monthly.answer":"Yes, you can pay monthly for your account. Choose the monthly option on the pricing page and you will be able to pay on a per month basis. The monthly plan is not discounted so if you are looking to save, we recommend the yearly plan.","pricingPage.faq.new.rightPlanForMe.question":"Which pricing plan is right for me?","pricingPage.faq.new.rightPlanForMe.answer":"We understand that each organization is unique, requiring specific features to support its workflows and projects. Above you can see the features included in the different plans to support your needs. If you need help in choosing the right plan for you, check out \u003ca href='https://monday.com/blog/product/monday-com-pricing-which-plan-is-right-for-you/' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003ethis article\u003c/a\u003e or reach out to our \u003ca href='https://monday.com/sales/contact-us?from=pricing\u0026source=Website%20-%20Contact%20Sales' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003esales team\u003c/a\u003e.","pricingPage.faq.new.howDoesOurPricingWork.question":"How does our pricing work?","pricingPage.faq.new.howDoesOurPricingWork.answer":"Our pricing is based on 2 variables: the feature plan you’d like to use, and the number of users on the platform. Once you’ve decided on the feature plan and users, choose your preferred subscription payment: month-to-month or annual. Payment is made in one upfront installment (so if you purchase a plan for one year, you will pay for one year upfront).","pricingPage.faq.new.changedMyMind.question":"What if I change my mind?","pricingPage.faq.new.changedMyMind.answer":"If you’ve paid for a yearly subscription in the last 30-days, and need to cancel your account, you are entitled to a prorated refund. We will automatically refund you the remaining balance from your original purchase. Simply cancel the account from the Admin section, and your account will be automatically refunded. If you have any questions, you can always reach out to \u003ca href='mailto: support@monday.com' target='_blank'\u003esupport@monday.com\u003c/a\u003e","pricingPage.faq.new.discount.question":"Do you offer any discounted plans?","pricingPage.faq.new.discount.answer":"Yes, through choosing a yearly plan, you will receive an 18% discount.","pricingPage.faq.new.students.question":"Does monday.com offer plans for students?","pricingPage.faq.new.students.answer":"Yes, our \u003ca href='https://monday.com/lp/students/' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003eStudent Program\u003c/a\u003e offers great opportunities and options for students and student organizations who would like to implement monday.com in their classes. University/college students, student organisations, fraternities, and sororities can all join the student programs.","pricingPage.faq.new.nonProfits.question":"Does monday.com offer plans to nonprofits and NGOs?","pricingPage.faq.new.nonProfits.answer":"monday.com is a proud supporter of organizations that do great things around the world. That’s why we offer discounted pricing for qualified nonprofit organisations. \u003ca href=\"https://monday.com/nonprofits\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eClick here\u003c/a\u003e to find out more about our nonprofit plan and pricing.","pricingPage.faq.new.manageBilling.question":"How can I manage my billing?","pricingPage.faq.new.manageBilling.answer":"If you are an admin of your account, you can access your purchase history, invoices, payment details, plan type, and more. Learn how to manage your billing details \u003ca href='https://support.monday.com/hc/en-us/articles/360018098000-How-to-manage-my-billing-' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.","pricingPage.faq.new.changePlan.question":"Can I change my plan?","pricingPage.faq.new.changePlan.answer":"You can make changes to your plan at any time by changing your plan type and adding and removing users (Note that post the refund period, we offer no refunds for downgrades). To change your plan, simply go into the Admin section and click on the Billing option. From there, click on 'change plan', pick the desired plan, and enjoy!","pricingPage.faq.new.security.question":"How secure is monday.com?","pricingPage.faq.new.security.answer":"The security of our customer’s data is our top priority. monday.com is built with strict security requirements and protocols to secure your data, such as ISO/IEC 27001 and ISO/IEC 27018, and is undergoing annual security audits and assessments. We use high physical, procedural, and technical security measures to preserve the integrity and security of your data, as well as adhering to the strictest data protection laws.","pricingPage.faq.new.paymentMethods.question":"What payment methods do you accept?","pricingPage.faq.new.paymentMethods.answer":"We accept the following payment methods: All the major credit cards (excluding debit cards) - Visa, Master Card, American Express, Discover, Diners Club, JCB, Carte Bleue, Union Pay. You can also purchase your monday.com subscription with PayPal. (Note this may be subject to change depending on your location.)\u003cbr\u003e We accept invoices for Enterprise orders that meet a minimum fee - Feel free to reach out to \u003ca href='mailto:support@monday.com' target='_blank'\u003esupport@monday.com\u003c/a\u003e for more information.","pricingPage.faq.new.mobile.question":"Do you have mobile apps?","pricingPage.faq.new.mobile.answer":"Yes, the platform is available on both IOS and Android devices. You can download them on the Apple or Google Play Stores. Learn more \u003ca href='https://support.monday.com/hc/en-us/articles/115005317225-Is-there-an-iPhone-iPad-tablet-and-or-Android-mobile-app-' rel='noopener noreferrer' target='_blank'\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.","pricingPage.faq.products.rightPlanForMe.answer":"Work needs are unique, so each kind of project and workflow requires its own set of features. Explore different features in a 14-day free trial for each of the plans above. If you need help in choosing the right plan for you, \u003ca href='https://monday.com/sales/contact-us?from=pricing\u0026source=Website%20-%20Contact%20Sales' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer'\u003eour sales team is here to help\u003c/a\u003e.","pricingPage.faq.products.whatIsWorkMgmt.question":"What is monday work management?","pricingPage.faq.products.whatIsWorkMgmt.answer":"monday work management provides you with the core building blocks you need to manage your work with monday.com. Tackle any process, project, or workflow - and scale and adapt it as your needs evolve.","pricingPage.faq.products.whatUseProductsFor.question":"What can I use monday products for?","pricingPage.faq.products.whatUseProductsFor.answer":"Monday products are end-to-end products to run the core of your business. These products are industry-specific tailored products, which includes pre-built workflows and designate features, designed for every aspect of your team's needs. Sales teams use monday CRM to manage their entire sales cycle. Marketing and creative teams use monday marketer to manage marketing and creative processes all in one place. Product, design and R\u0026D teams use monday dev to build agile workflows to support product development. Project managers use monday projects to run, manage and track your projects and portfolios.","pricingPage.faq.products.howProductsWorkTogether.question":"How do all products work together?","pricingPage.faq.products.howProductsWorkTogether.answer":"You can use all Work OS products in collaboration with each other by easily switching between them inside the platform. Add more products at any time or move your data between products to have all your work under one ecosystem.","pricingPage.faq.products.diffBetweenWorkMgmtAndProducts.question":"What is the difference between monday work management and products?","pricingPage.faq.products.diffBetweenWorkMgmtAndProducts.answer":"Work management equips you with the core building blocks you need to build any workflow from scratch. Work OS products complement work management by providing you with industry-specific workflows and features to get your started, instantly.","pricingPage.faq.products.howPricingWork.answer":"Our pricing structure is based on the feature plan you’d like to use, and the number of seats you purchase. First, choose the work management plan that's right for you and your team. Then, add any tailored monday products (monday marketer, monday CRM, monday dev or monday projects) in order to complement your solution. Lastly, choose the number of seats that fits your team and your preferred subscription. Payment is made in one upfront installment (yearly) or month-to-month.","pricingPage.plans.free.title":"Individual","pricingPage.plans.free.title.name_free":"Free","pricingPage.plans.basic.title":"Basic","pricingPage.plans.standard.title":"Standard","pricingPage.plans.pro.title":"Pro","pricingPage.plans.enterprise.title":"Enterprise","pricingPage.plans.enterprise.cta.talkToSales":"Talk to sales","pricingPage.plans.student.title":"Student","pricingPage.plans.npo.title":"Nonprofit","pricingPage.freeForDurationOfStudies":"Free for the duration of your studies","pricingPage.plans.npo.discount":"70% discount","pricingPage.tierDescriptions.student":"For students looking to keep track of their tasks and work.","pricingPage.tierDescriptions.individual.new":"For individuals looking to keep track of their work","pricingPage.tierDescriptions.individual.new.name_free":"For small teams looking to keep track of their work","pricingPage.tierDescriptions.basic.new":"Manage all your teams’ work in one place","pricingPag